    <p>Vitafusion dominates the multivitamin gummy market with over 52,000 reviews and a 4.7-star average that speaks to both product quality and taste. At $0.13 per serving for 75 days of coverage, it is the most affordable daily multivitamin gummy available from a nationally recognized brand. The nutrient profile covers the most critical gaps — vitamin D3 at 25mcg (125% DV), vitamin B12 at 6mcg (250% DV), and zinc at 5mg (45% DV) — making it an effective nutritional baseline for most adults.</p>

