    <p>Nature Made earns the #2 position through its USP Verification — the most rigorous third-party testing available in the supplement industry. The USP seal means that an independent laboratory has confirmed that each gummy contains exactly what the label claims, dissolves properly, and is free from harmful contaminants. For women specifically, the formula includes 400mcg of folate (critical for women of childbearing age) and elevated biotin levels for hair and nail health.</p>

